maintext:
CRANSTON, R.I. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday evening’s drawing of the Rhode Island Lottery’s “Wild Money” game were:
10-13-17-27-33, Extra: 35
(ten, thirteen, seventeen, twenty-seven, thirty-three; Extra: thirty-five)
Estimated jackpot: $68,000
